articles.title: Thailand Hits Cambodia With F-16s as Deadly Border Clash Erupts - Bloomberg.com
articles.description: Thai F-16 fighter jets struck military sites in neighboring Cambodia as a border dispute between the Southeast Asian nations, stretching back decades, erupted in fresh violence that killed at least 11 people.
